		<div id="mw-content-text" class="mw-body-content mw-content-ltr" lang="en" dir="ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><dl><dd>For discussing a specific main page, please see <i><a href="./Talk:Categorized_Main_Page" title="Talk:Categorized Main Page">Short view</a>  (<a href="./Talk:Categorized_Main_Page/archive" title="Talk:Categorized Main Page/archive">archive</a>)</i>, or <i><a href="./Talk:Expanded_Main_Page" title="Talk:Expanded Main Page">Expanded view</a></i></dd></dl>
